ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectDesignation of Regulatory Provisions for Purposes of Enforcement (Migratory Birds Convention Act, 1994) Regulations
PrecisDESIGNATION OF REGULATORY PROVISIONS FOR PURPOSES OF ENFORCEMENT (MIGRATORY BIRDS CONVENTION ACT, 1994) REGULATIONS in order to complete the fine regime introduced by the Environmental Enforcement Act and designate offences in regulations under the Migratory Birds Convention Act, that are subject to the regime of minimum fines and higher maximum fines in order to ensure that fines reflect the seriousness of designated offences. ,
